Hello,

It seems you are using a wrong version of PCI utils... Which one are you
using? (You can get it by typing "/sbin/lspci --version" as root)

Could you send me the files /usr/include/pci/pci.h
and /usr/include/pci/config.h? It seems they do not define some types as
they should...

Have you the same problem with Mandrake, or another one?

Best regards,

Nicolas

